description:
List event exports executed by the system

Only the following filter combinations are supported:

| Handler | Result | EventTarget | EventType | OrderID |
| ------- | ------ | ----------- | --------- | ------- |
| any     | any    | null        | null      | null    |
| null    | any    | null        | null      | null    |
| any     | null   | any         | any       | null    |
| null    | null   | any         | any       | null    |
| null    | null   | null        | null      | any     |

This service won't return the actual attempts. Use `GetEventExportAttempts` for that.
